{"tid":2137502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不要說「方艙醫院」，試着說「社區治療設施」","createTime":"2020-08-03T03:42:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T04:46:46.000Z","uid":154004,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3d5c57895aa02ec57f91ea22a1d607f025d5c25f","tid":2137502,"uid":154004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T03:42:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WZFMeBn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWZFMeBn.jpg&h=e4e49416&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EKa8sW2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEKa8sW2.jpg&h=271bcf56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n區家麟 ：//<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\">一直覺得，「方艙醫院」的說法好哽耳。</span></strong>朋友問，為什麼「方艙醫院」叫「方艙醫院」？於是我去慧科與百度查了一下「方艙」名字的源流。<br />\n<br />\n「方艙」一詞是軍事術語，早見於二十多年前，是軍用物資一種，例如「野戰醫院方艙」、「通訊方艙」等，泛指用堅固物料砌成、方便移動的組件，內裡則砌好各式醫療器材或通訊裝備等，一應俱全，方便行軍。維基則指「方艙」意思為預製組件的結構，不過綜觀中國大陸的報章用法，「方艙」幾乎只見於有關軍事設施的報道，民間用的組合屋或預製組件的構築物，絕少用「方艙」。<br />\n<br />\n名字的源流，各地有約定俗成的用法，內地用「方艙醫院」，香港大可不必跟隨。<br />\n<br />\n首先，現時在亞博館的臨時設施，不是「方艙」，不是「方型」，也沒有「艙」，詞不達意，令人摸不着頭腦。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">再者，若用「方艙醫院」之名，容易惹來誤會，以為是內地援建產物，根據醫管局講法，是由醫管局與亞博館合力興建，沒提過有內地援兵。剛到香港的七位內地人員，乃幫忙檢測工作，不是建醫院。社交媒體上看到很多醫護大聲疾呼，亞博館的設施是香港自己籌劃興建，非「國家隊援建」，不要相信黨媒講法。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n若跟隨香港官方，即特區政府及醫管局的說法，亞博館那個叫「社區治療設施」，收治輕症病人，看來不能稱為「醫院」。<br />\n<br />\n當然，遲些國家隊援建兵團來到，可能在亞博館旁的空地建醫院，到時叫什麼名字，就不是「受助者」去選擇。<br />\n<br />\n而我慢慢明白為何一直覺得「方艙醫院」一詞有古怪，可能因為是日常生活中出現軍事修辭，感到不甚舒泰。 //<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E8%AA%AA-%E6%96%B9%E8%89%99%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2-%E8%A9%A6%E7%9D%80%E8%AA%AA-%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80%E6%B2%BB%E7%99%82%E8%A8%AD%E6%96%BD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%25AA%25AA-%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%2589%2599%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A2-%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E7%259D%2580%25E8%25AA%25AA-%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E7%2599%2582%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E6%2596%25BD%2F&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F4429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=9e92fcdd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%25AA%25AA-%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%2589%2599%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A2-%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E7%259D%2580%25E8%25AA%25AA-%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E7%2599%2582%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E6%2596%25BD%2F&h=6446173c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E8%AA%AA-%E6%96%B9%E8%89%99%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2-%E8%A9%A6%E7%9D%80%E8%AA%AA-%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80%E6%B2%BB%E7%99%82%E8%A8%AD%E6%96%BD/</a>"},{"pid":"de4ccbf156dcf359fba375e06d5dfc19015fa08b","tid":2137502,"uid":154004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T03:42:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"40e970bc6bedd5052c8830095f2de18d13e1cc03","tid":2137502,"uid":154004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T03:42:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca510398dd26faf5c17a63f059e6399f0d540ab2","tid":2137502,"uid":154004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T03:43:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"381bf52d7ed23d8ea397d8070c0f6ed5cc07dcc9","tid":2137502,"uid":26618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T03:45:45.000Z","msg":"推，唔想日後大陸人又話要不是中國點點點。"},{"pid":"cfc8f4e4f3a29ced67f23ee83ed7c4d86a5395d1","tid":2137502,"uid":268271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T03:45:53.000Z","msg":"醜死！ 柒婆幾百張床都叫賊共幫！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a801cc1441aaac7197917b16f61b9b78a1ba7bc0","tid":2137502,"uid":158457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T0